{"tid":1776513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃Gphone入」立即解決台灣戰線危機","createTime":"2019-12-09T14:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:56:13.000Z","uid":102527,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"198273ddc04e776936fe04ad8f84ed876ce963a1","tid":1776513,"uid":102527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"1. 立即誠懇道歉用詞不當，並非冒犯<br />\n<br />\n2. 抬高台灣，用「予國」等既字眼，令台灣人感覺你有誠意而唔係怕得罪佢地<br />\n<br />\n3. 承認依加既形勢好危急，講錯小小野都會俾人放大，同時稱讚台灣人有智慧判斷中共既分化策略，大家都係抗共既前線，即使處境未必一樣，但都有住同樣既敵人，希望未必唔會俾中共進一步分化關係<br />\n<br />\n4. 提醒台灣人中共既滲透分化策略，叫佢地注意唔同討論區有冇明顯帶風向既行為，澄清從來冇提出過所謂既3大訴求，小心有心人偽造文宣<br />\n<br />\n5. 講番其實都係擔心在台手足既安全<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論，歡迎任插"},{"pid":"d9507a5f2549f77ea13ddf9a99958ba876c7022f","tid":1776513,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cae678ba6e8ade783557938995782539638a1048","tid":1776513,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係下一個checkpoint<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf65b9d34f3986a2f7a23ddf658560ed2b8b556e","tid":1776513,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係下一個checkpoint<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"77bdb810326013f88b793a8e203cf612effc56c7","tid":1776513,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係下一個checkpoint<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"064003e36f42cb356188be04173c5e9d284b9865","tid":1776513,"uid":102527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d61ad69c72f5bc7a1a9303